---
name: translate
description: Translates text from one language to another
model: claude-sonnet-4-6
provider: anthropic
temperature: 0.2
max_tokens: 1024
vars:
  text: string
  target_lang: string
  source_lang: string = auto-detect
---

Translate the following text to {{target_lang}}.
Source language: {{source_lang}}.

Only return the translated text — no explanations, no notes.

Text:
{{text}}
